        <div id="getting-started">
          <h2>Three possible use-cases for reminderss:</h2>
          
          <ol>          
            <li>
              <h2>Sites that don't have RSS, but should</h2>
              <p>Can't subscribe?  Set a reminderss, so that you can return to the site at a later date</p>
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <h2>Sites you want to browse the old-fashioned way</h2>
              <p>The rss feed may not be exactly what you want, or too much data, or you just enjoy viewing the page in its layout glory</p>
            </li>

            <li>
              <h2>Reminders</h2>
              <p>You need to buy milk, and you want to be reminded of this in your RSS Reader of choice.</p>
            </li>
          </ol>
